detail.name: Piccolo (Mini) : DA
detail.effect: [On Play] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and reduce its cost by 1 for the turn. Then, if your opponent has a Battle Card with a cost of 2 or less, draw 1 card.

detail.name: ピッコロ(ミニ)：DA
detail.effect: 【登場時】相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、コスト-1。その後、相手のコスト2以下のバトルカードがある場合、カード1枚を引く。
